display_long_description:
# 🥎 Welcome to Spinball: The New 360 MR Tennis Experience

Dive into the thrill of a fresh mixed-reality ball game that fits right into your living room!

# 🥎Step into the ring and compete against players from around the world in epic 1v1 racket battles!
[media]

# 🥎Face Sparx the AI bot in multiple difficulty levels
[media]

# 🥎Test your skills and improve your game with the Spinball ball machine!
[media]

# 🥎Play minigames to improve your skill in the Spinball Academy
[media]

# 🥎Customize your equipment in the locker room, climb the ranks, and become a Spinball All-Star.
[media]

**Main features:**
* Online ranked/unranked game modes
* Solo mode - Face Sparx in multiple difficulty AI levels
* Spinball Academy - Multiple training modes
* Spinball Friends - Add and invite your friends for private matches
* Main Locker - Customize your rackets, balls and characters
